programme.desc: Un inquilino se niega a abandonar su apartamento en un barrio que se está gentrificando. Su empeño en seguir viviendo en el mismo lugar lo enfrenta de manera violenta a los inversores inmobiliarios y a las autoridades.

programme.title: Sol ardiente
programme.desc: Un resort costero sufre una ola de calor abrasadora. El agua escasea, y la violencia está a punto de estallar. Un joven es el encargado de proteger la casa vacía de una familia adinerada mientras están fuera, ante el riesgo de saqueos.

programme.title: Señora presidente
programme.desc: Una presidenta se siente abrumada tras un año en el cargo, decidiendo escaparse en secreto en la noche, disfrazada, y poder pasar desapercibida, pero lo que comienza es un romance inesperado con un hombre que no tiene idea de su verdadera identidad.

programme.title: La confesion
programme.desc: La hermana de Jeanne le confiesa en el lecho de muerte que, hace 15 años, Youssef fue encarcelado injustamente por el asesinato de Julie, la mejor amiga de Jeanne. La hermana le suplica que haga justicia y encuentre al verdadero homicida.

programme.title: La asesina perfecta
programme.desc: La principal sospechosa de un asesinato podría ser la responsable de la muerte de la hija de un detective que se debate entre la justicia o la venganza.

programme.title: Ninja Assassin
programme.desc: A rogue (Rain) enlists the help of the Europol agent (Naomie Harris) whose life he saved to bring down the clan of hired killers who trained him as an assassin.

programme.title: Burn
programme.desc: Melinda is a lonely and unstable gas-station attendant whos tired of being overshadowed by her more confident and outgoing co-worker. When a robber holds up the station at gunpoint, Melinda tries to make a connection with the desperate thief.

programme.title: Law and Order: Special Victims Unit
programme.desc: A dead newborn leads detectives to a dermatologist, then a serial pedophile.

programme.title: Hollywood One on One
programme.desc: Hollywood celebrities give insight into their personal and professional lives, and open up about upcoming projects.

programme.title: The Samaritan
programme.desc: After many years in prison, a former grifter (Samuel L. Jackson) tries to go straight, but the son (Luke Kirby) of his former partner insists on learning the game and relieving a feared gangster (Tom Wilkinson) of $8 million.

programme.title: Mad Max 2: The Road Warrior
programme.desc: Loner lawman Mad Max (Mel Gibson) fights barbarian bikers for gasoline in the wasteland of the future.

programme.title: Vertical Limit
programme.desc: After his fathers death, Peter (Chris ODonnell) quits climbing and his sister Annie (Robin Tunney), becomes a top climber. After an expedition Annie is leading is stranded by inclement weather, Peter has to assemble a rescue team to save them.

programme.title: Deep Impact
programme.desc: As a comet is on a collision course with earth, humans have to prepare for their survival. They randomly select eight hundred thousand people to be saved in order to keep the human race alive.

programme.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire

programme.title: Speed Racer

programme.title: The Grudge
programme.desc: Two detectives investigate a murder scene in a haunted house that passes on a ghostly curse to those who dare enter it.

programme.title: Saint Maud
programme.desc: Maud, an unstable, newly devout hospice nurse, becomes obsessed with saving her dying patients soul -- but sinister forces and her own sinful past threaten her holy calling.

programme.title: House of Wax
programme.desc: Friends (Elisha Cuthbert, Chad Michael Murray) become stranded in a town where murderous twins entomb their victims in wax.

programme.title: Blumhouses Fantasy Island
